        "content": "<h3 style=\"text-align:center\">The Right Architecture: Critical For Successful Ecommerce.&nbsp;<br />\nDon&#39;t be left behind. Start your ecommerce journey today&nbsp;and grow fearlessly with flexible and future-proof architecture.</h3>\n\n<p>Whether you&#39;re looking to embark on your digital commerce journey, considering changing your existing solution provider, or thinking about phasing out a home grown, legacy solution that you&#39;ve outgrown &ndash; you need to build your new solution on the most flexible and scalable architecture available,<strong>&nbsp;as using the wrong technology can greatly slow down your ecommerce business.&nbsp;</strong><br />\n<br />\nWhile the potential problem of outgrowing your ecommerce platform is not top of mind- it can happen sooner than you think. Ecommerce is a rapidly changing industry and constantly evolving. You can&#39;t predict what trend will be crucial for your business next year, or further into the future.&nbsp;<strong>The only thing you can do to be prepared in this environment is to rely on architecture that is designed for constant and fast-paced change.&nbsp;</strong></p>\n",
